What’s crazy about doing the no liquor for 60 days, it never was about the drinking too much alcohol. It was me standing on self discipline knowing that temptation was gone be in my face every night every 5 minutes “take a shot ”. I stayed stiff on it and it help to say no to other shit I needed to cut out of my life so at the end of the day it was healthy for me physically and mentally and I encourage anyone to challenge their self to do something that will hold you accountable for 60 days in a self discipline way and it will payoff I promise. ❤️🤞🏾

(If you offered me a shot during these 60 days and I turned it down please repost/share I lost count in August 😅)

Transparent moment… I’ve waited patiently for 3 years before deciding to curate another nightlife spot weekly. After “TH” my son was born and I lost my mother all within those 3 weeks so I sat back and just focused on DJing. I feel like the city needs more balance it’s too much of the same sh*t industry wise and the focus has gotten away from the consumer and the experience. A lot Promoters out here trying to control people lives and what they do on their free time a whole bunch of weirdo sh*t. I’m just here to make it fun again so here 11/25 #TrillSaturdays Dallas Social !!! We bringing a different experience every week and having a PARTY!! If you don’t like PARTIES THIS NOT FOR YOU! ❤️🤞🏾🛝
From Houston With Love 🤘🏾❤️

social_posts.post_text: It’s kinda surreal to even think that I could visit another country, make my presence felt not only as a DJ but also as a man of great character and to be trusted by business owners and create partnerships to curate a entire weekend named after my brand. If I told someone that was my goal at the beginning of the year they probably would say “Trill you done lost your mind” 😅 But Obviously what they don’t know about me is I’m not afraid to go for it. I’d rather try failing than not trying at all and that’s who I’ve always been. Special thank you to @24k.cancun for believing in me and connecting the dots. Also to my partners @classpmyers @tyznation @kenznation who believed in the vision off one conversation on a yacht in Cancún. It’s not no Fyre Fest it’s the real thing and it’s one of my biggest challenges so far but I accept. 🇺🇸🇲🇽❤️ #TrillFestCancun2024
